<h1>About</h1>
<p>
	Pasteboard is a quick and simple image sharing web app driven and developed by me, Joel Besada. If you are a developer and would like to contribute to (or learn from) the source code of this app, make sure to check out the <a href="https://github.com/bobvandevijver/pasteboard" target="__blank" data-track="Github (modal)">Github repo</a>.
</p>
<p>
	Images uploaded to Pasteboard are publicly available but not broadcasted, meaning it is up to you to decide who you share the images with.
</p>
